รายละเอียดงาน
-Be responsible for the overall operation and management of the Group's overseas security, and continuously optimize the terminal security strategy and protection system;
-Manage the security compliance of the desktop terminal, including the issuance, execution and effect evaluation of the desktop management platform strategy;
-Undertake the construction and optimization of intranet access and zero trust access control system to prevent illegal access and horizontal mobile risks;
-Be responsible for daily virus detection and poisoning terminal treatment of overseas terminals;
-Carry out daily data leakage prevention audit, identify abnormal behavior and potential leakage risks, and promote closed-loop rectification;
-Cooperate with security incident response, investigation, evidence collection and report analysis;
-Track the development trend of data security and zero-trust architecture, and promote the continuous evolution of the capabilities of DLP, EDR and related platforms;
-Formulate and improve relevant systems and processes such as terminal security, data protection, desktop control and intranet access.
คุณสมบัติผู้สมัคร
- Bachelor degree or above, major in information security, computer, network, etc.
- More than 3 years of experience in information security, with practical experience in terminal security, data leakage prevention, zero trust, intranet access and other fields;
- Familiar with the deployment, operation and maintenance and strategy optimization of mainstream antivirus, DLP, EDR, desktop management system, access control (NAC), zero trust architecture and terminal security products;
- Have strong security incident analysis, problem investigation and risk identification capabilities, and can independently undertake audit and emergency response work;
- Strong communication, coordination and documentation skills, experience in information security management of large groups or cross-regional enterprises is preferred;
- Holders of CISSP, CISP, CISA, CEH and other information security certifications are preferred.
